interfaces.free:
openplc-cli device add "tempsens" "10.0.0.2" "502"
openplc-cli device add "fan" "10.0.0.3" "502"
openplc-cli program add "/shared/fan_control.st" "fancontrol" "control the fan"
openplc-cli settings set Start_run_mode true
/opt/OpenPLC_v3/start_openplc.sh &

scripts.startup:
openplc-cli device add "tempsens" "10.0.0.2" "502"
openplc-cli device add "fan" "10.0.0.3" "502"

openplc-cli settings set Start_run_mode true
/opt/OpenPLC_v3/start_openplc.sh &
